Srinivas D.R. has taken charge as financial adviser of Mangaluru Electricity Supply Company. He had joined the then Karnataka Electricity Board in 1985 as assistant accounts officer. He holds MBA degree.Previous stintsEarlier he had served in Chitradurga, Davangere, Haveri, Kalaburagi, Tumakuru and Ballari in various capacities.